Conventions
- Keep provider abstraction clean; support local Ollama with fallbacks.
- Preserve Swedish language optimizations in prompts and STT/TTS.
- Follow weights: authenticity 40%, concreteness 30%, depth 30%.
- Ensure deterministic JSON outputs for scoring/explanations where consumed downstream.
